CAMPAIGN CHANGES
------------------------------------------

-AI not so aggressive, but still challenging
-AI invasion missions and convoys become rarer as the player captures more locations
-Fixed missions with "terminateIfUnsafe":false, now set to true
-Fixed logic error with location safety check for AI
-Terrain alignment fixes (ships spawning on land shouldn't be as common now)

GAME MECHANICS AND BUG FIXES
------------------------------------------

-Changed sonar modifiers related to sea states
-Significantly lowered passive sonar factor values for most ships (In layman's terms, ships are now generally harder to pick up on passive sonar)
-Lowered chance of flooding spreading when a flooded cell is being repaired.
-AI aircraft should no longer fly off in a single direction or swarm a location in the campaign map
